    ('Liger Zero (Naked)',NULL,100,300,2,NULL,5,NULL,'mountain, forest','"Naked": During your Custom Phase, this Zoid can change into a Liger Zero type Zoid in the same stack with the "CAS" ability. "Wild Cry": Declare usage. Roll for accuracy against all Zoids within a 1-square radius, and paralyse them if the result is 5 or higher. If you roll a 6, deal 200 damage as a critical bonus.','F'),
