    ('Liger Zero',NULL,200,600,4,NULL,5,'straight +2','mountain, forest','"CAS (Changing Armour System)": During your Custom Phase, if this Zoid changes into a Liger Zero type Zoid in the same stack with the "Naked" ability, recover 200 HP. "Strike Laser Claw (Photon Claw)": When using a melee attack, the critical bonus becomes +300.','F'),
